Pix Transmissions Ltd (PTL) is an Indian manufacturer of belts and related mechanical transmission products, that are used in diverse industrial, agriculture, and automotive applications. Headquartered in Mumbai, Maharashtra, the company has manufacturing facilities in Hingna and Nagalwadi, Nagpur.In 2021, PTL reported consolidated revenue of INR 4 billion. The company has also listed in the Bombay Stock Exchange in the year 1989.